                    <item>
                        <title>v1.9.0</title>
                        <description><![CDATA[<ul>
  <li>Restored distributable BitBar</li>
  <li>BitBar now requires OS X 10.7 to fix a crash on refresh and wake from sleep</li>
  <li>Added support for single click action from the status bar (<code class="highlighter-rouge">href</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">bash</code> and <code class="highlighter-rouge">refresh</code>)</li>
  <li>Added support for separators in sub menus</li>
  <li>Added update check (Preferences menu will show you when there’s a newer version available)</li>
  <li>Various other bug fixes</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
