                    <item>
                        <title>v1.6.0</title>
                        <description><![CDATA[<ul>
  <li>Added <a href="https://github.com/matryer/bitbar/blob/master/Docs/DistributingBitBar.md">distributable BitBar</a> to allow you to bundle a BitBar app with plugins, and distribute a tamper free version.</li>
  <li>Added ability to refresh plugins remotely via the <a href="https://github.com/matryer/bitbar/blob/master/Docs/URLScheme.md">URL scheme</a> - #149 and #216</li>
  <li>Integration with Slack - please join us: <a href="https://getbitbar.herokuapp.com/"><img src="https://getbitbar.herokuapp.com/badge.svg" alt="Slack Status" /></a></li>
  <li>Added ability to <a href="https://github.com/matryer/bitbar/blob/master/Docs/DistributingBitBar.md#settings">hide Preferences menu</a>.</li>
  <li>Small UI improvements based on feedback from lovely users just like you.</li>
  <li>
    <p>Updated dependencies to fix crash and memory leak.</p>
  </li>
  <li>See a <a href="https://github.com/matryer/bitbar/compare/v1.5.1...master">complete list of all changes in this release</a></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
