                    <item>
                        <title>v1.5.1</title>
                        <description><![CDATA[<p>Features:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Added <code class="highlighter-rouge">trim=false</code> option to give plugin authors control of whitespace - #182</li>
  <li>Added <code class="highlighter-rouge">alternate=true</code> option to allow option key menu items - #218</li>
  <li>Tasks now run in background (preventing menu bar items from locking) - #181</li>
  <li>Plugins will reset on wake from sleep - #184</li>
  <li>Added URL scheme for opening and downloading plugins - #224</li>
</ul>

<p>Other:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Work to address duplicate items - #21</li>
  <li>Updated “Browse plugins…” link to getbitbar.com</li>
  <li>Improved docs</li>
  <li>“Open at login” was getting reset every time - now it’s remembered - #169</li>
  <li>Warnings and static analyzer errors are resolved</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
